{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "反常光譜", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "16-1", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "庸人的救濟", "storyInfo": "最後一位聖愚在狂妄的自辯中走向消亡。多年前，Mantra曾被內衛糾纏。現在，為尋找失聯的Raidian小隊，她與羅德島眾人再度面對內衛留下的痕跡。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$formal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g12_deitygrypherburgmeeting", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "cr"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>烏薩斯帝國議會</><p=2>1099年秋</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1982_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰能告訴我，陛下還要放任這場鬧劇到什麼時候？一天、一個月，還是一年？", "name": "煩躁的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真是受夠了，維多利亞人早就學會控制天災了，就連那些蠻荒的魔族都造出了可以在天上飛的戰艦。", "name": "煩躁的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們，卻要把時間浪費在商議如何處置這個弄臣小丑？", "name": "煩躁的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1982_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人，這是陛下的仁慈……畢竟現在還是有不少民眾相信這個瘋人擁有某種高尚的品德，陛下也願意將這場審判公之於眾。", "name": "恭敬的近侍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1982_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "期限是七天，而到剛才為止……已經過去六天又二十一個小時了。", "name": "恭敬的近侍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1982_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愚蠢——真是愚蠢！難道我們還要繼續忍受這些汙言穢語，指望最後一夜的鐘聲能讓那個小丑清醒嗎？", "name": "煩躁的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1982_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，大人，恐怕是的。不過好消息是，在鐘聲敲響後，帝國議會將在這裡開始投票。", "name": "恭敬的近侍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1982_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那個時候，您就不必再忍受這一切了。從今往後都不必了。", "name": "恭敬的近侍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1982_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……我當然知道。", "name": "煩躁的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，滾開吧。就算這丑角之死是注定的，在他真正被埋進土裡或者被燒成灰燼之前……", "name": "煩躁的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都還會是烏薩斯僅存的聖愚。", "name": "煩躁的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armyboots_walk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "ar"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "ar", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沉默的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armyboots_walk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "ar"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "ar", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.6}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？我是不是看錯了？好像是近衛軍的制服——", "name": "煩躁的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "cr"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他又回來了？才休息了五分鐘……在之前的演講中，他甚至連一口水都沒喝！", "name": "驚訝的貴族"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一場演講——", "name": "狂熱的貴族"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wtchkgopenftstp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都注視著一個衣衫襤褸、格格不入的傢伙大步走到議會大廳的中央。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他背脊挺直，肢體卻鬆弛，臉上看不出任何對將來的擔憂，或為自己的生存而掙扎的痛苦。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五分鐘前，他才剛在這裡發表了一通演講——關於愛，關於寬恕，關於他如何原諒所有決定殺死他的人。"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "六天的遊說已使聽眾都深覺疲憊，而他卻彷彿完全不受影響，只是一抬手，四周就驟然安靜。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他開口，甚至仍然帶著笑意。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我親愛的朋友們，或者視我為敵的人們，相信我們都清楚，這就是最後了。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此接下來我不會繼續談論愛是何種情狀，也不會再大聲宣揚我原諒你們將對我施行的所有錯誤。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我將談論——將來，一個不識字的盲人眼中的將來。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……荒謬……", "name": "沉默的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們需牢記，敘述歷史是無上崇高的權力，這樣的權力同樣容易令人盲目。", "name": "聖愚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十年來，陛下將他的榮光與萬民分享，他的子民卻沒有做好準備以迎接福澤。", "name": "聖愚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從不質疑陛下的仁慈，但是不合時宜的仁慈堪比毒藥。", "name": "聖愚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叛亂的集團軍和北原的感染者，無疑都證明了這一點。", "name": "聖愚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卑劣者昂起叛逆的頭顱，將他們骯髒的血塗抹在神聖的土地上；狂妄的學者宣稱掌握真理，有害的言論如毒蟲啃食無辜的心靈。", "name": "聖愚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無知的傲慢瘋狂滋長，讓人民忘記謙卑，讓帝國忘記慈愛。偉大的帝國與她的子民離心離德。", "name": "聖愚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到過去與將來——並非因為智慧，我只是一個愚人，可是未來的走向早已寫在過去的車轍中。", "name": "聖愚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絲毫不後悔宣揚我見到的那個將來，哪怕這是將我送上審判台的緣由，我也不得不繼續宣揚我看到的預言。", "name": "聖愚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了烏薩斯的終局，我看到了一個偉大帝國的陷落。", "name": "聖愚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "cr"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是今天我站在這裡，我懇請陛下，去阻止這一切發生。如果這需要用到我不值一提的性命，那就拿去吧。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果需要更多的血來洗刷烏薩斯的不潔，我也懇請陛下這麼做——一切都是為了更偉大的事業，為了屬於烏薩斯的永恆榮光。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這場審判後——無論它以怎樣的結果落幕，我都將開始我的聖途。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我將一遍又一遍地重申謙卑的美德，試圖以這種方式喚回人心，還有帝國的榮光。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許你們會認為我僭越，但我既不領導軍隊，也不制定律法。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許你們認為我病入膏肓，但我既非瘋子，亦非狂人。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的雙手比流浪者更空，我的穿著比感染者更破。我所做的一切——我的過錯，只是使人看到不同的歷史，傾聽不同的聲音。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "使我們不嘗試粉飾痛苦，深埋地底的傳統將再度被發掘。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "使我們不嘗試淡化殘酷，沉寂已久的呼喊得以振聾發聵——", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那時，也許，也許我們偉大帝國的未來將煥然一新——所有憤怒都趨於平靜，無數罪孽將得到寬恕，而一切痛苦……", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都會由純潔的忍耐化解。", "name": "聖愚"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_heartbeat", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>烏薩斯北原荒野</><p=2>■■■■年</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_speedline", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——跑！快跑！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像其他人那樣，一直往前，不要回頭！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 4.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_snowpowder", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 3.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_094", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我們跑不掉……我們跑不掉的！就算跑出烏薩斯，也是死路——", "name": "絕望的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_094"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "power": 3.0, "times": 30.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳——咳咳咳！", "name": "絕望的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_094"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呼吸得太用力了，雪會嗆進你的喉嚨——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowfootstep", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "s"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血會嗆進他的喉嚨。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_094"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳呃——", "name": "慌亂的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_094"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "power": 4.0, "times": 40.0, "isblock": "true", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-50", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,-100", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼快就掙脫出來了？！怎麼——怎麼可能——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很聰明，但還不夠。你先前向我投射的幻景，某種程度上也是你自己的經歷。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，你錯在不知道那幻景裡的痛苦對我們來說就像妄圖撬動山峰的羽毛。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過這至少展現了你的能力。你有資格成為“它”的替代品。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過，我對你們嘗試玩弄邪魔力量的行為一無所知，也不感興趣。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並不是一個邀請，而是最後通牒。在我厭倦前，你當然能從我手中救下他們一次、兩次……甚至三次。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在我已經厭倦了。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……別再靠近了，除非你想帶走的只是我的屍體。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的“聲音”不再穩定，你開始懷疑自己。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並非聖愚，卻使用它的力量。代價是？", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道你在說什麼。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬事萬物都有代價，你也快接近你的盡頭了。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許，那個盡頭是我們會一起死。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有我們。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你沒有聽見。或者你只是已經沒有多餘的精神去關注更多？", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒有聽見那些雪地上的腳步聲，沒有聽見你就算同歸於盡也想保護的人……只是一群苟且的蟲子。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實他們從來不敢離開故土太遠。說著不願背棄國家，懷揣極度的僥倖，即使逃亡也刻意蹣跚，或是乾脆朝著死亡折返歸來。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為離開這裡，他們就無法確認自己的存在，即使這存在帶來的只有絕望。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很可惜，你的告誡全無用處。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像你告訴他們的。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“不要回頭”。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_darkmagic", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bdevilmgc", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃——！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳！咳——咳——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想為烏薩斯帶來一位連身體機能都被破壞殆盡的聖愚，這會浪費很多時間，即使你本身的能力超群也並不划算。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我再次建議你選擇放棄掙扎，跟我離開。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也再說一次，我不知道你說的“聖愚”是什麼，也對成為它毫無興趣！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，就算我現在和你離開，那感染者呢？那些被你們驅趕的……走投無路的……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會有自己的命運。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想你必須“說”得更明確一點。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，不。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安靜，緊繃，四周皆然。在完整的“話語”自腦海中浮現前，雪依舊飄落，那黑色身軀向前邁步的動作卻凝滯了。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下一簇新雪尚未觸及大地，漆黑的薄霧已在蔓延。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_phantommagic", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blacksmoke_01", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“留下。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他突然失去了繼續前進的意願。剝離了理智的另一半認知，則等待著先前的圖景再度出現。"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "故技重施……", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是沒有。什麼也沒有。"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有毫無來由的停滯，只有漆黑自他周身不斷散出，從薄霧累積成厚重的塵灰。"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像下了一場黑色的雪。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是——但我沒有——", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊。", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我體內的邪魔發生了輕微洩漏，你竟然能利用我的力量，反過來控制我？", "name": "“皇帝的利刃”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是讓你困於你體內的穢物包含的……幻影，讓你直視你自身。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "？？？", "content": "不要試圖做無謂的掙扎，否則……"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "？？？", "end": "true", "content": "咳咳。", "joined": "不要試圖做無謂的掙扎，否則……咳咳。"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則，你就會死。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "？？？", "content": "在你自己的“國度”裡……"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "？？？", "end": "true", "content": "咳——咳咳咳！！", "joined": "在你自己的“國度”裡……咳——咳咳咳！！"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉睡吧……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "power": 4.0, "times": 40.0, "isblock": "true", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-50", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,-100", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093#5", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天啊，這、這——", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#5"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子……孩子！你還好嗎？那個黑漆漆的怪物難道還在追我們——", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#5"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093#4"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——啊！", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#4"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……咳、咳呃。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不會……再追你們了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093#2"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#2"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走，離開這裡，往南去，在他“醒過來”之前。這次真的不能再回頭了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們必須離開這裡才能活……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093#2"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您、您說什麼？他不會再追我們了？", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#2"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼意思？", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#2"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093#5"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是說，您勸服了不通人情的巫怪？", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#5"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說了，快走！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093#2"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走……走去哪裡？", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#2"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳道士大人說過，“背棄故土者永不配自稱為人”。我們……我們不願那樣！", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#2"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不願背棄陛下、背棄烏薩斯，也不願背棄您……", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#2"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您竟然真能使他不再追來……您救了我們，做到了不可能做到的事，卻還是不願意告訴我們您的名字嗎？請問您到底是誰？", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#2"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不重要，我……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093#4"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，其實——", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#4"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實您真的就是那位消失已久的聖愚？", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#4"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……什麼……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093#4"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但聖愚應該在聖駿堡富麗堂皇的宮殿裡，在陛下的身邊。", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#4"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，沒錯！如果您原本就不屬於這裡，我們只是竊取了這份恩賜，那被懲罰，也是理所當然。", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093#3"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我們應當忍耐”、“我們應當承受”……“我們應當平靜”！但我們什麼也沒有做到……", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#3"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算這樣，您還是庇護了我們這些有罪的靈魂。", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#3"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您一定就是聖愚。否則，您不會擁有這樣的胸懷，向感染者也伸出援手的、同等的博愛。", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#3"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_093"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，您的名字就只有可能是那一個了，不是嗎？", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個您不願我們稱頌的名字，那個所有聖愚共同擁有的名字——", "name": "畏縮的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "cr"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_avg_dreamrite_intro", "key": "$m_avg_dreamrite_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“迦弗里伊爾”。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footsteps_flock", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 6.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 2.0, "fillfrom": 0.6, "fillto": 0.6, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i02", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "y": 70.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 200.0, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迦弗里伊爾、迦弗里伊爾……", "name": "感染者"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是聖愚，是我們的聖愚回來了！", "name": "感染者"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“聖愚”，是故事書裡的那個嗎？", "name": "感染者"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 6.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.6, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 2.0, "fillfrom": 0.6, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i02", "screenadapt": "coverall", "x": 0.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是媽媽說，就算不在我們身邊，就算我們得了石頭病，也會愛著我們的那個嗎？", "name": "感染者"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，是她！她回來了！她屏退了惡人，庇佑了凡人，這都是只有聖愚才能做到的事！", "name": "感染者"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖愚拯救了我們，聖愚——", "name": "感染者"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i02", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人群，吵嚷，無數雙手不斷向她湧來。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們攀扯彼此，像潮水陣陣撲向海岸，只為能夠觸及受崇奉者身上的一片衣角，哪怕那只是與他人並無不同的粗布衣衫。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被包圍的人再也無力支撐，無力思考。抽搐著以膝蓋接觸雪面的那個瞬間，她幾乎就快這樣癱軟在地。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是不行。內衛還在這裡，想要利用她去殺死更多人的劊子手還在這裡，她不能閉眼，不能……放棄。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳——咳呃——", "name": "“迦弗里伊爾”？"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃啊——", "name": "“迦弗里伊爾”？"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剎那間她甚至以為自己早已廢棄的舌根再度與口腔共振，真切地發出了聲音，但身體卻只是悄無聲息地蜷縮，直到越來越小，越來越小。"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她忍耐著，等待這痛楚熄滅。"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖愚——", "name": "感染者"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並非聖愚，卻有代價。"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而就連被誤認的人本身也不知道這荒謬舉動的代價有多少。也許有時候，“不明代價”，本身就是一種代價。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "